{{wikidata|Q577034|Laconic phrases}}
From {{der|en|la|Lacōnicus||Spartan}}, from {{der|en|grc|Λακωνικός||Laconian}}. [[Laconia]] was the region inhabited and ruled by the Spartans, who were known for their [[brevity]] in speech.

